						Sven Oxtoby is the building performance assessment expert at Greenbuild Consultants responsible for generating and maintaining standard procedures and reporting formats. Prior to joining Greenbuild Consultants, Sven worked as consulting engineer at WSP on heating, ventilation and air-conditioning, also specialising in thermal and daylight modelling. Sven holds a BSc in Mechanical Engineering from the University of Cape Town.
					</p>
